  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dba \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dda \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dd6 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The father who endangered the child's life was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kuliapitiya Police say that a father who made a video threatening the life of the five-year-old child to bring his wife who is abroad has been arrested.",
        "On the last 11 days, the suspect father took the child to a deserted house on the land, took a sharp knife and created the video in such a way that the life of the 5-year-old male child is unsafe. In order to save the child's life, the suspect father made a video saying that the wife should come and also forwarded the video to the foreign employment agency that supported the wife and her to go abroad through WhatsApp technology. .",
        "However, after the relevant video was brought to the attention of Kuliapitiya Headquarter Chief Inspector Jayaweera Rajapaksa through the relevant foreign employment company, considering the high risk situation of the child, he immediately implemented a police strategy to arrest the suspect."
      ],
